<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title><%= title %> | Deployment Flow</title>

    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/favicon.png" />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        body {
            font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            background: #f1f5f9; /* Light slate */
            color: #0f172a; /* Dark slate */
        }

        /* HEADER */
        header {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #1e40af, #2563eb);
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 70px 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
        }

        header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
        }

        header p {
            margin-top: 12px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            opacity: 0.95;
        }

        /* SECTION */
        .section {
            padding: 50px 20px;
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: auto;
        }

        .section h2 {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            color: #1e3a8a;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .section p {
            line-height: 1.7;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #1e293b;
        }

        /* FLOW CARDS */
        .flow-container {
            margin-top: 40px;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 25px;
        }

        .flow-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            transition: 0.3s ease;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 5px solid #2563eb;
        }

        .flow-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-6px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 28px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
        }

        .flow-card img {
            width: 65px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        /* CODE BLOCK */
        .code-block {
            background: #0f172a;
            color: #38bdf8;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-top: 25px;
            overflow-x: auto;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
        }

        .code-block code {
            color: #a5f3fc;
        }

        /* FOOTER */
        footer {
            background: #1e3a8a;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-top: 40px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        /* RESPONSIVE */
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            header h1 {
                font-size: 2.3rem;
            }
            .section h2 {
                font-size: 1.8rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<%- include("partials/header", { title: "Welcome to NodeAuth" }) %>

<header>
    <h1>About My Deployment Flow</h1>
    <p>CI/CD pipeline using GitHub Actions, Docker, ECR, ECS Fargate & Load Balancer</p>
</header>

<section class="section">
    <h2>Overview</h2>
    <p>
        This project uses a fully automated CI/CD deployment pipeline.  
        Every push to <strong>main</strong> builds a Docker image, pushes it to ECR, updates ECS task definitions,  
        and redeploys the service behind an Application Load Balancer.
    </p>
</section>

<section class="section">
    <h2>Deployment Flow</h2>

    <div class="flow-container">
        
        <div class="flow-card">
            <img src="https://i.ibb.co/Kz0Sgbt/github.png" alt="GitHub">
            <h3>1. GitHub Actions</h3>
            <p>Push triggers workflow → builds Docker image → deploys to AWS.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="flow-card">
            <img src="https://i.ibb.co/1KFfF29/docker.png" alt="Docker">
            <h3>2. Docker Image Build</h3>
            <p>GitHub builds the Docker image using your Dockerfile.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="flow-card">
            <img src="https://i.ibb.co/KsNYnVz/aws-ecr.png" alt="ECR">
            <h3>3. Amazon ECR</h3>
            <p>The Docker image is pushed to Amazon Elastic Container Registry.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="flow-card">
            <img src="https://i.ibb.co/2kKXzWM/task.png" alt="Task">
            <h3>4. ECS Task Definition</h3>
            <p>Task definition updates automatically with the new image.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="flow-card">
            <img src="https://i.ibb.co/KwKyBj8/ecs.png" alt="ECS">
            <h3>5. ECS Fargate</h3>
            <p>Fargate deploys the updated container serverlessly.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="flow-card">
            <img src="https://i.ibb.co/4JQZcZW/lb.png" alt="Load Balancer">
            <h3>6. Load Balancer</h3>
            <p>ALB routes traffic and keeps the app always available.</p>
        </div>

    </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
    <h2>GitHub Actions Workflow</h2>

    <div class="code-block">
<pre>
<code>
<%= `name: Deploy to Amazon ECS

on:
  push:
    branches: [ "main" ]

env:
  AWS_REGION: ap-south-1
  ECR_REPOSITORY: node/mk-pipeline
  ECS_SERVICE: mk-task-definition-service-8pqtz7f5
  ECS_CLUSTER: mk-cluster
  ECS_TASK_DEFINITION: .aws/task-definition.json
  CONTAINER_NAME: mk-container

jobs:
  deploy:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest

    steps:
      - uses: actions/checkout@v4

      - uses: aws-actions/configure-aws-credentials@v1
        with:
          aws-access-key-id: \${{ secrets.AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID }}
          aws-secret-access-key: \${{ secrets.AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY }}
          aws-region: \${{ env.AWS_REGION }}

      - uses: aws-actions/amazon-ecr-login@v1

      - name: Build Docker Image
        run: |
          docker build -t ... (trimmed)
` %>
</code>
</pre>
    </div>
</section>

<%- include("partials/footer") %>
</body>
</html>
